<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>ZipZap Activation Email</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
      /* Base Styles */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222;
      }

      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      /* Layout */
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #fff;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      /* Button */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 12px 24px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to ZipZap!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>
          Thank you for registering as a seller on ZipZap! We’re thrilled to
          have you join our marketplace.
        </p>
        <p>
          Here’s your one-time verification code to activate your seller
          account:
        </p>
        <h1><%= otp %></h1>
        <p>
          This code will expire in 5 minutes, so please enter it on the
          activation page to complete your registration.
        </p>
        <p>If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>For any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Wishing you success,</p>
        <p><strong>The ZipZap Team</strong></p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://zipzap.com">Visit ZipZap</a> |
          <a href="mailto:support@zipzap.com">Contact Support</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
